== 私人生活 ==
哈桑·鲁哈尼的父亲阿萨多拉·鲁哈尼是在伊朗[[塞姆南市|塞姆南市]]的[[巴剎|巴剎]]经商的商人，而他的母亲目前住在塞姆南。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.shomanews.com/News/?Id=7169 |title=Personal life of Hassan Rouhani |accessdate=2013-06-15 |archive-date=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927085259/http://www.shomanews.com/News/?Id=7169 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

1968年，鲁哈尼与Naemeh Arabi结婚，後育有二子二女。其長子於1992年4月[[自杀|自杀]]身亡，并葬于[[德黑兰市|德黑兰市]]的贝赫斯特·扎赫拉公墓。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.shomanews.com/News/?Id=6984 |title=Who Rouhani's son was death? |accessdate=2013-06-15 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615195039/http://www.shomanews.com/News/?Id=6984 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

除了[[波斯语|波斯语]]，他还能流利地讲[[英语|英语]]和[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]。拥有英国[[格拉斯哥卡利多尼安大學|格拉斯哥卡利多尼安大學]][[法律|法律]]学[[博士|博士]]学位<ref >{{cite web |url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/06/15/309169/rohani-becomes-irans-new-president |language= |title=Rohani becomes Iran’s new president |publisher=PressTV |date=2013-06-16 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616040552/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/06/15/309169/rohani-becomes-irans-new-president/ |archive-date=2013-06-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref >{{cite web |url=https://www.rferl.org/a/mahdavi-azad-interview-rohani/25022981.html |language= |title=Former Aide Says Iranian President-Elect 'Is Not Superman' |publisher=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty |date=2013-06-20 |accessdate=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308231227/http://www.rferl.org/a/mahdavi-azad-interview-rohani/25022981.html/ |archive-date=2017-03-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

